      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Lowercasing --> transform all the chars in text into lowercase\n\nPunctuation and digit removal --> removes all punctuation and numbers\n\nText encoding --> converts EMOJI into texts\n\nNOTE : Do normmalization based on ur project goals.",
